  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/93b9b3f3b6bac7e163502f4d7954b28a.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black Submarine</strong> is a thrilling underwater adventure that puts you in control of a powerful, ultra-technological submarine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2086, the Pacific Ocean harbors profound secrets and unimaginable dangers. Navigate treacherous waters, face deadly enemies, and discover deep secrets beneath the sea. This game combines intense action, exploration, and strategy, offering a unique and immersive experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to plunge into this submerged journey?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Main Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/ab8b3f071864640830d4783375e89d12.avif?t=1765757384\" width=780 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single-Player Campaign:</strong> Embark on a journey that explores stories inspired by the folklore of the underwater world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/17c15f2c409f0fce8352bee5cf6005ff.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/17c15f2c409f0fce8352bee5cf6005ff.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/17c15f2c409f0fce8352bee5cf6005ff.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tactical Combat:</strong> Use laser weapons and equipment to overcome waves of dangerous sea creatures.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/9200c5242a708b14b0b1d3965a73a69e.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/9200c5242a708b14b0b1d3965a73a69e.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/9200c5242a708b14b0b1d3965a73a69e.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underwater Exploration:</strong> Dive into underwater caves and a sunken pirate ship in search of treasure and valuable resources.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/1978a5edea50f48169bf33eaf83002e1.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/1978a5edea50f48169bf33eaf83002e1.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/1978a5edea50f48169bf33eaf83002e1.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Submarine Customization:</strong> Upgrade your submarine to prepare for future challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get ready to dive!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Black Submarine: deep seek</strong>, each dive is a unique adventure filled with dangers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to uncover the hidden secrets in the depths of the Pacific?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive in now and discover the mysteries that await!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/93b9b3f3b6bac7e163502f4d7954b28a.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black Submarine</strong> is a thrilling underwater adventure that puts you in control of a powerful, ultra-technological submarine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2086, the Pacific Ocean harbors profound secrets and unimaginable dangers. Navigate treacherous waters, face deadly enemies, and discover deep secrets beneath the sea. This game combines intense action, exploration, and strategy, offering a unique and immersive experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to plunge into this submerged journey?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Main Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/ab8b3f071864640830d4783375e89d12.avif?t=1765757384\" width=780 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single-Player Campaign:</strong> Embark on a journey that explores stories inspired by the folklore of the underw